Source: runtipi-docker-service
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Hat Labs <info@hatlabs.fi>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), curl, ca-certificates, python3
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/hatlabs/runtipi-docker-service

Package: runtipi-docker-service
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, docker-ce-cli, docker-compose-plugin
Description: Runtipi homeserver orchestrator with systemd integration
 Runtipi provides a user-friendly web interface for managing Docker
 containers and self-hosted applications. This package installs the
 runtipi-cli tool and configures it as a systemd service.
 .
 Runtipi provides:
  - Container management through web UI
  - App store with 300+ pre-configured applications
  - Simple Docker orchestration for self-hosting
 .
 The web interface is accessible on port 80 after installation.
